♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

85
00:05:12,910 --> 00:05:14,630
I’ve spent my whole life with you

86
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:17,680
even before we grow old.

87
00:05:19,150 --> 00:05:20,720
I’m lucky,

88
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,890
