89
00:05:21,890 --> 00:05:27,030
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

90
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:31,830
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

91
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,660
I don’t need to struggle to an old age.

92
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,070
